item.title: Models
item.dc:creator: @deathschaos9 DeathsChaos9
item.description:
@deathschaos9 wrote:

Download a model and place it into a model folder, than go into class 8 or class 5 and add your ints, after that compile and log on to your client, than do ::addmodel or add model or what ever your command is than say the model ID and it will say it loaded, close the cleint reload and you should have a fully working model. this is server help btw, not client. Keep that in mind and post in the right place next time.
